Subject: File system
Description: Does not seem that the file system monitoring is working properly. Some permissions seem to be off when you compare it to the folder permissions on the server.
What_We_Know__c: Some permissions are off when compared to the folder permissions on the server because the Bulk Import is not working as it should.
Next_Steps__c: If the scan fails with the same error, "T2 database does not match the T1 database," I will delete the T2 and rerun the Permission scan
Solution_Comment__c:
Expand the Bulk Import > Configure and Query Properties
Under the Query Selection, click on Maintenance
Under Maintenance, select Repair; next, select the host and run the Repair.
